OL,5, Scotland's top law officer has         
OL,6, apologised to victims of the Horizon   
OL,7, scandal.                               
OL,9,FLord Advocate Dorothy Bain said Post   
OL,10,FOffice workers had been failed by the  
OL,11,Fcriminal justice system.               
OL,13,FShe said the Crown Office and          
OL,14,FProcurator Fiscal Service (COPFS),     
OL,15,Fwhich has sole responsibility for      
OL,16,Fprosecuting cases in Scotland, had been
OL,17,Fmisled by the Post Office.             
OL,19,FMs Bain said she understood the "anger"
OL,20,Fof victims.                            
